# Sequence Diagram: AgentOS Install with Agent-Specific Directmermaid
sequenceories

```Diagram
    participant U as User
    participant I as agentos-install.sh
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant P as Project Dir

    Note over U,P: Scenario: Install with agent-os=opencode
    
    U->>I: ./agentos-install.sh install --project-dir /tmp/demo --agent-os opencode
    I->>I: validate_inputs()
    I->>FS: ensure_dir(PROJECT_DIR)
    FS-->>I: dir created
    
    I->>FS: copy_extension(opencode, PROJECT_DIR)
    FS-->>I: .opencode created
    
    I->>I: copy_agentos_specific_assets(PROJECT_DIR, opencode)
    
    Note over I: Check source dirs in project root
    
    alt ../rules exists
        I->>FS: copy ../rules -> .opencode/rules
    end
    
    alt ../skills exists
        I->>FS: copy ../skills -> .opencode/skills
    end
    
    alt ../workflows exists
        I->>FS: copy ../workflows -> .opencode/commands
    end
    
    I->>I: copy_specialization_assets(PROJECT_DIR)
    I->>I: generate_agents_md(PROJECT_DIR)
    I->>I: print_report()
    I-->>U: Installation complete
    
    Note over U,P: Result: Files in agent-specific dirs
    Note over U,P: - .opencode/rules/*
    Note over U,P: - .opencode/skills/*
    Note over U,P: - .opencode/commands/*
```

