## Container Diagram: AgentOS Structure

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Source["Project Root (this repo)"]
        direction TB
        AS["agentos-install.sh"]
        EXT["extensions/"]
        RULES["rules/"]
        SKILLS["skills/"]
        WF["workflows/"]
    end
    
    subgraph Install["Install Process"]
        IP["copy_agentos_specific_assets()"]
        MAP["Agent Directory Map"]
    end
    
    subgraph Dest["Target Project"]
        direction LR
        
        subgraph OpenCode[".opencode/"]
            OCR[".opencode/rules"]
            OCS[".opencode/skills"]
            OCF[".opencode/commands"]
        end
        
        subgraph Cursor[".cursor/"]
            CUR[".cursor/rules"]
            CUS[".cursor/skills"]
        end
        
        subgraph KiloCode[".kilocode/"]
            KCR[".kilocode/rules"]
            KCS[".kilocode/skills"]
            KCF[".kilocode/workflows"]
        end
        
        subgraph Agent[".agent/"]
            AR[".agent/rules"]
            AS[".agent/skills"]
            AW[".agent/workflows"]
        end
    end
    
    AS --> IP
    EXT --> IP
    RULES --> IP
    SKILLS --> IP
    WF --> IP
    
    IP --> MAP
    
    MAP -->|opencode| OCR
    MAP -->|opencode| OCS
    MAP -->|opencode| OCF
    
    MAP -->|cursor| CUR
    MAP -->|cursor| CUS
    
    MAP -->|kilocode| KCR
    MAP -->|kilocode| KCS
    MAP -->|kilocode| KCF
    
    MAP -->|antigravity| KCR
    MAP -->|antigravity| KCS
    MAP -->|antigravity| KCF
    
    MAP -->|default| AR
    MAP -->|default| AS
    MAP -->|default| AW
```
